    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/ab7a7a0413038dfadad208bbcceda4ce.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>外星人边疆是一款开放世界的第三人称设计游戏。在致命的外星荒野中探索、搜索和开采资源<br><br><br><br>……只要你能在与成群结队的嗜血外星人的战斗中幸存下来。收集战利品并进行升级，成为银河<br><br><br><br>系中最危险（也是最富有）的探矿者！<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/Frenetic_Combat.gif?t=1677231837?t=1761276276\" /></span><br>在与致命的外星动物群的残酷斗争中，用你的方式进行抢夺、冲刺、滑翔和盘旋。 在刺激肾上腺<br><br><br><br>素、子弹地狱般的第三人称战斗中杀出一条血路，感受游戏的无尽乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/fe85e8b272d42f1a6439400e2405b12d.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏内含100种特殊物品、升级和能力，每个回合都有机会以创造性和意想不到的方式发现战利品<br><br><br><br>并对其进行组合升级，让您即使面对最可怕的外星人也能释放毁灭性的力量。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/81a70d10256508f485b9b74cd2f7dcd7.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为星际探矿者，您不仅要探索广阔的开放世界，还要尝试去改变它。从在深山中建造隧道到在<br><br><br><br>地面上设置大型采矿设备，您创造的每一处建筑都会改变景观并为您提供宝贵的升级和设备奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.poster.avif?t=1761276276\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.webm?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2330810/extras/af4cb9bf9ade1ee0ed90e85a12ed37a6.mp4?t=1761276276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用您的喷气背包、推进器和悬浮滑板探索没有小地图引导的程序化开放世界。阅读风土地貌，<br><br><br><br>探索世界的每一个角落，揭开陌生星球的神秘面纱。",
